PrecisOrder authorizing (1) the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the DECISION OF THE CANADA-EUROPEAN UNION JOINT CUSTOMS COOPERATION COMMITTEE CONCERNING THE MUTUAL RECOGNITION OF THE PARTNERS IN PROTECTION PROGRAMME OF CANADA AND THE AUTHORIZED ECONOMIC OPERATOR PROGRAMME OF THE EUROPEAN UNION; or (2) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers, authorizing the individuals mentioned in the order, to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the Decision.
